LCL oxygenated.

234
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,380
Releasing airlock.

235
00:13:30,109 --> 00:13:32,919
Why am I piloting this thing again,
even though my father's not here?

236
00:13:35,782 --> 00:13:37,332
Even though I got beat up?

237
00:13:41,487 --> 00:13:44,416
Hey, I need to talk to you,
privately, you know?

238
00:13:44,891 --> 00:13:45,591
What for?

239
00:13:45,758 --> 00:13:47,428
Just give me a second, okay?

240
00:13:47,727 --> 00:13:48,957
Well, okay.

241
00:13:50,063 --> 00:13:51,403
Class rep!

242
00:13:51,664 --> 00:13:52,304
What?

243
00:13:52,465 --> 00:13:54,485
We both hafta go to the john!

244
00:13:54,834 --> 00:13:57,294
You were supposed to use the bathroom
before you came here.

245
00:13:58,204 --> 00:13:59,544
So, what's this about?

246
00:13:59,806 --> 00:14:02,206
I've got to see it, at least once in my life.

247
00:14:02,608 --> 00:14:03,747
You mean the battle up there?

248
00:14:03,976 --> 00:14:06,996
Nobody knows when the enemy
will come the next time.

249
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:09,848
Kensuke, are you serious?

250
00:14:09,849 --> 00:14:12,129
Do not use
If we let this opportunity escape us,
we may lose it forever!

251
00:14:12,518 --> 00:14:15,038
Please, help me unlock the gate.

252
00:14:15,455 --> 00:14:16,855
But you'll get killed if you go out there.

253
00:14:17,123 --> 00:14:18,763
You don't know if that'll happen,
even if we stay here.

254
00:14:19,058 --> 00:14:20,928
If I could be killed anyway,
I'd rather see it first.

255
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:24,100
Idiot. What do you think Nerv's for?

256
00:14:24,564 --> 00:14:26,964
And what is Nerv's most important weapon?

257
00:14:27,367 --> 00:14:29,416
It's the robot the new kid pilots.

258
00:14:29,769 --> 00:14:31,759
He protected us the other day,

259
00:14:32,105 --> 00:14:34,915
but you hit him pretty hard. Twice!

260
00:14:36,242 --> 00:14:39,551
If he refuses to pilot the robot,
we're all going to die.

261
00:14:40,546 --> 00:14:44,146
Don't you have a duty to watch him fight?

262
00:14:45,084 --> 00:14:46,574
Ah, whatever.

263
00:14:48,020 --> 00:14:50,949
You sure are upfront about what you want,
ain't you?

264
00:14:53,659 --> 00:14:55,968
Shinji, are you ready to head out?

265
00:14:56,362 --> 00:14:56,972
Yes.

266
00:14:57,130 --> 00:15:01,230
Listen to me. Neutralize the enemy's AT field,
then fire a volley from the pallet gun.

267
00:15:02,235 --> 00:15:03,815
Do it just like we practiced.
Can you handle that?

268
00:15:04,103 --> 00:15:05,337
Yes.

269
00:15:05,338 --> 00:15:06,208
Launch!

270
00:15:26,125 --> 00:15:29,145
Cool! All my efforts really paid off!

271
00:15:29,629 --> 00:15:31,119
Oh! This is what I've been waiting for!

272
00:15:39,572 --> 00:15:40,502
There it is!

273
00:15:43,709 --> 00:15:45,677
The AT field has been deployed.
Target in the center, pull the switch.

274
00:15:45,678 --> 00:15:47,848
Do it just as planned, okay, Shinji?
Target in the center, pull the switch.

275
00:15:48,214 --> 00:15:49,064
Right.

276
00:15:56,222 --> 00:15:58,062
You idiot! You hid the enemy
with your own smoke!

277
00:16:09,068 --> 00:16:10,877
What the hell?! He's already losing!

278
00:16:11,204 --> 00:16:12,133
It's all right.

279
00:16:12,338 --> 00:16:13,767
I'm sending you a spare rifle.

280
00:16:14,674 --> 00:16:15,524
Take it!

281
00:16:16,876 --> 00:16:18,746
Shinji? Shinji?

282
00:16:19,779 --> 00:16:21,239
Oh, man!

283
00:16:21,514 --> 00:16:23,684
Being beaten up must have
really messed him up.

284
00:16:24,050 --> 00:16:25,069
Shut up!

285
00:16:46,939 --> 00:16:48,139
The umbilical cable's been severed!

286
00:16:49,575 --> 00:16:51,776
Eva has switched to its internal
battery power source.

287
00:16:51,777 --> 00:16:54,267
4 minutes, 53 seconds
of activation remaining.

288
00:17:03,256 --> 00:17:04,185
It's comin' this way!

289
00:17:09,262 --> 00:17:11,997
Shinji, are you all right? Shinji!

290
00:17:11,998 --> 00:17:12,831
Damage report?

291
00:17:12,832 --> 00:17:14,122
No problems detected. He can make it.

292
00:17:25,211 --> 00:17:26,731
Shinji's classmates?

293
00:17:27,012 --> 00:17:28,153
What are they doing there?

294
00:17:40,927 --> 00:17:42,357
Why won't he fight?

295
00:17:42,628 --> 00:17:44,588
Because we're here?

296
00:17:44,931 --> 00:17:46,571
He can't move because of us!

297
00:17:46,866 --> 00:17:49,996
Unit 01 activation time remaining,
3 minutes 28 seconds.

298
00:17:52,939 --> 00:17:55,189
Shinji, let them into the cockpit!

299
00:17:57,410 --> 00:17:59,400
Once you've got them,
make a temporary retreat.

300
00:17:59,745 --> 00:18:00,594
We'll regroup!

301
00:18:00,780 --> 00:18:04,149
You think you can allow unauthorized
civilians into the entry plug?!

302
00:18:05,284 --> 00:18:06,484
I'm authorizing it.

303
00:18:06,719 --> 00:18:08,499
You're exceeding your authority,
Captain Katsuragi!

304
00:18:10,790 --> 00:18:13,220
Unit 01's remaining activation time,
3 minutes.

305
00:18:13,626 --> 00:18:17,666
Hold Eva on your current commands
and eject the entry plug. Hurry up!

306
00:18:21,233 --> 00:18:23,223
You two! Get in! Hurry!

307
00:18:24,837 --> 00:18:26,007
What the... It's water?

308
00:18:26,906 --> 00:18:28,426
My camera! My camera!

309
00:18:32,612 --> 00:18:34,252
Abnormal conditions occurring
in the nervous system!

310
00:18:34,547 --> 00:18:36,767
Of course. It's because you've allowed
two foreign bodies into the plug.

311
00:18:37,149 --> 00:18:39,289
They're introducing noise
in the nerve impulse systems!

312
00:18:46,359 --> 00:18:47,879
Now! Retreat!

313
00:18:51,864 --> 00:18:54,199
Recovery route 34, retreat to
the east side of the mountain.

314
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,567
Hey, new kid, she said, "Retreat!"
Recovery route 34, retreat to
