315
00:18:55,568 --> 00:18:56,528
Hey, new kid, she said, "Retreat!"

316
00:18:56,736 --> 00:18:58,696
I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away.
New kid!

317
00:18:59,438 --> 00:19:00,548
I mustn't run away!

318
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,610
Progressive Knife engaged!

319
00:19:06,712 --> 00:19:09,022
Obey my orders, Shinji! You've got to retreat!

320
00:19:09,915 --> 00:19:10,735
Shinji!

321
00:19:16,088 --> 00:19:17,138
That idiot...

322
00:19:35,741 --> 00:19:38,261
Unit 01, activation time
remaining, 30 seconds!

323
00:19:39,412 --> 00:19:41,222
28...27...

324
00:19:41,547 --> 00:19:43,687
26... 25...

325
00:19:48,587 --> 00:19:50,017
14...13...

326
00:19:50,289 --> 00:19:51,809
12..11..

327
00:19:52,091 --> 00:19:53,841
10... 9...

328
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:55,680
8..7..

329
00:19:55,961 --> 00:19:57,451
6... 5...

330
00:19:57,730 --> 00:19:58,460
4.

331
00:19:58,631 --> 00:19:59,391
3.

332
00:19:59,565 --> 00:20:00,205
2.

333
00:20:00,366 --> 00:20:01,216
1.

334
00:20:08,874 --> 00:20:10,544
Eva Unit 01, activation ceased.

335
00:20:10,843 --> 00:20:12,683
The target is completely silent.

336
00:20:55,521 --> 00:20:58,151
It's been three days.

337
00:20:59,391 --> 00:21:01,911
You mean, since we were chewed out?

338
00:21:02,628 --> 00:21:05,378
No, since he stopped comin' to school.

339
00:21:05,831 --> 00:21:06,971
Who's "he"?

340
00:21:07,199 --> 00:21:09,189
The new kid, the new kid.

341
00:21:10,102 --> 00:21:11,712
I wonder what he's been doin' since then?

342
00:21:12,004 --> 00:21:13,083
Are you worried about him?

343
00:21:13,706 --> 00:21:16,045
No, not exactly worried.

344
00:21:16,442 --> 00:21:18,902
Toji, for someone who's so tactless,
you're pretty stubborn.

345
00:21:19,979 --> 00:21:22,589
If you had apologized to him back then,

346
00:21:23,015 --> 00:21:25,475
you wouldn't have had to agonize
over it for three days.

347
00:21:25,885 --> 00:21:28,495
Here, this is the new kid's phone number.

348
00:21:29,421 --> 00:21:31,291
If you're so worried, why don't you call him?

